These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, aconite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsaconite is between the fan of pop and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Flower      | daisy | aconite | lily |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, fonseca
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the dannemann-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Cigar   | dannemann    | fonseca        | havana |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo, golf
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing     | golf |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, march
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Birthday   | february  | march     | june |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, prince, pall-mall
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar   | prince | pall-mall     | vegafina |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
House: cottage, futuristic, tower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the tower house and the cottage house##2
2. the cottage house is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| House   | cottage  | futuristic   | tower        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
City: prague, new-york, paris
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person traveling to prague is between the person eating pineapple and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| City   | new-york | prague | paris     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
3 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, poker
1. the person watching satire movies is the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing snooker is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, blues, punk
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the fan of punk and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Music-Genre       | punk | d&b | blues  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

