The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, crime, mystery
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the person watching mystery movies and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | documentary    | crime |

