.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, red
1. the person who likes red is between the person drinking fanta and the person who likes purple##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Color       | fuchsia  | red | purple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
